@startuml object_risk_to_fca_request_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Object Risk To FCA Request Signal Flow\n(object risk + decel intent -> FCA FCW/AEB request publish)

participant "ADAS / object-risk /\ndecel inputs" as RiskCtx #F4F7FB
participant "FCA\ncollision warning owner" as FCA #E8F7E8
participant "FCA state bus" as FcaBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers / downstream AEB users" as Obs #E8F0FE

== Risk Inputs ==

RiskCtx -> FCA : objectTrackValid\nobjectRiskClass\nobjectTtcMin\ndecelAssistReq\nfailSafeMode
FCA -> FCA : if riskInputStale then\nobjectTrackValid = 0 / objectRiskClass = 0
FCA -> FCA : if decelInputStale or failSafeMode >= 2\nthen decelAssistReq = 0
FCA -> FCA : fcwState = calcFcwState(...)
FCA -> FCA : aebRequest =\n(decelAssistReq == 1 and objectRiskClass >= 4 and failSafeMode < 2) ? 1 : 0
note right of FCA
Representative gating inputs
- objectTrackValid
- objectRiskClass
- objectTtcMin
- decelAssistReq / failSafeMode
end note

== FCA Publish ==

FCA -> FcaBus : frmFcaStateMsg\nFcwState / AebRequest / DecelAssistReq
FCA -> FcaBus : ObjectRiskClass / TtcBucket / SelectedAlertLevel
note right of FCA
Representative outputs
- FcwState
- AebRequest
- SelectedAlertLevel
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

FcaBus -> Obs : collision-warning readback /\naeb-request consumers

note over RiskCtx, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Object-risk and decel intent reach FCA
2. FCA decides FCW state and whether AEB request is allowed
3. FCA publishes collision warning and AEB request state
4. Downstream consumers observe the effective collision request posture
end note

@enduml
